personal.name: Ryan Gocal
personal.title: Freelance Android Developer
personal.shortBio: Greetings! I am a tech savy father of 2 boys and gamer! I am a shop manager during the day but at night, I'm a coffee drinking java code junky. I am a free lance android developer trying to look at things from a different angle and achieve things we havn't seen yet. I love tinkering with Android Home Launcher app interfaces.

work.title: Inventory Manager
highlights: Implemented several CI that improved workflow and safety for all employees

projects.title: Material Popup Menu
projects.description: My first android library published. It was a reboot of the context popup menu found in the original ADW Launcher code from android gingerbread. This revision included an up to date material attractive look with updated dynamic menus.

projects.title: Switchbar
projects.description: A simple toolbar widget for android that behaves like a switch that dynamically behaves to the action of the switch.

projects.title: Fluent Popup Menu
projects.description: A reboot of my first Material Popup Menu library with an updated look, feel and easy to use interface with some tricks up its sleave. Create a stylish popup view that inflates a menu, a tip or whatever you want. Alot of stylish material you based customization for all developers alike.

projects.title: Google Play Publisher Info Class
projects.description: A java file class I wrote to take advantage of a homebrew api to gather Google Play app information from its publisher.

projects.title: Launcher Ops
projects.description: An Ops like android app that allows users to manage and change their Launcher Apps on their device. Play detective and search installed launcher apps for any protective permissions, class items, services and ads.

projects.title: Carpenter
projects.description: Android app to manage installed Icon Packs and browse the contents of the apk. Save, extract and craft with the icons that have been provided to you and create your own resources! Quickly preview and apply icon packs to supported launcher apps.

projects.title: Drosera Launcher
projects.description: An Android Launcher app designed for gamers and handhelds! Currently in development...

projects.title: Sapphire Launcher
projects.description: My first custom android launcher based on Launcher2 code by Slim Roms.

projects.title: Sapphyx Launcher
projects.description: An Android Launcher that was based on Pixel Launcher code. GG Lawnchair Launcher...RIP

projects.title: Drywall
projects.description: My first Wallpaper app for Android that pulled wallpapers from a json file from my github. RIP

projects.title: Launcher Quick Tile
projects.description: A Quick Tile for Android that allows users to swap launchers faster than the android settings provides by default.
